Name: Dungeon Knight
About the game: A fun and simple pixel platforming puzzle game where you play as a small telekinetic knight, and your goal is to escape the dungeon in which you are held. Dungeon Knight Also has over 30 levels, along with constant updates, events, and new additions to the game.
